Mickey Carroll https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mickey_Carroll 0 Mickey Carroll (July 8, 1919 – May 7, 2009) was an American actor, who worked in radio and film, and was one of the last surviving actors who portrayed a munchkin in the 1939 film The Wizard of Oz.
